native communities and the agricultural development of the forest and forest rim regions; Decree Law 
No. 22175 (1978), arts. 7, 8, 10 and 11; and its implementing regulations under Supreme Decree No. 
003-79-AA (1979), arts. 4 and 5. 
</p>
<p> 
